data.description: Fabulous BRICK home on .75 cul-de-sac lot in BOXWOOD, chic and absolutely beautiful, priced to sell.  Formals, gleaming hardwoods, new lighting, updated kitchen with granite, cozy breakfast area, main level den with fireplace, and great for entertaining.  Enjoy the sunroom on main level, grill/dine on the newly extended deck, or frolic and play games on the turf play area.  Second level boasts nice master with pampering master bath, his/hers closets, three other bedrooms, plus nursery/office. Terrace level finished with family room, nice wet bar/kitchenette with granite, rec room, office/bedroom, full bath.  Nicely landscaped, storage building, neighborhood pool/playground, and so convenient. WOW!
